{"title":"研究生录取通知书","icon":"letter","shareable":true,"id":"newcomer/prepare/grad-admission-notice","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"录取通知书制作时间"},{"tag":"text","text":["录取通知书会拟录取名单公示期过后制作，给予一定时间修改邮寄人电话与地址，并于六月中旬左右发出。"]},{"tag":"card","cover":"$img/tab/admission.jpg","title":"录取查询","logo":"letter","url":"admission?type=search"},{"tag":"text","type":"info","text":["我校研究生录取通知书使用 EMS，速度会很快。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/prepare/grad-admission-bag.jpg","desc":"录取通知书","watermark":true},{"tag":"title","text":"录取通知书内容"},{"tag":"ul","text":["录取通知书 1 份","调档函 1 份"]},{"tag":"text","type":"warning","header":"强调","text":["❌不含手机卡、银行卡亦或校园卡","(⚠不要再问了...😑)"]},{"tag":"title","text":"学号"},{"tag":"text","text":["录取通知书编号即为学号，是以 2025 开头的十位数字，在通知书右下角。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/prepare/grad-admission-letter.jpg","desc":"录取通知书","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/prepare/grad-admission-letter-back.jpg","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/prepare/grad-admission-gift1.jpg","desc":"本子","watermark":true},{"tag":"img","src":"$img/prepare/grad-admission-gift2.jpg","desc":"书签","watermark":true}],"time":"2025 年 6 月 30 日 14:04:02"}